name: Puzzling Reality - by Asmodai Studios
blurb: The apocalypse has come, and physics is out of control. Regain control to either save the world or watch it burn. The choice is yours.

rewards.reward: SUPPORTER - You are a true humanitarian.  You get our sincerest thanks for helping out with our project and will be listed on our website!
CREDITED SUPPORTER - You'll get our sincere thanks and your name in the credits of the finished game listed as a "Supporter."

EARLYBIRD SPECIAL OWNER - You'll get the finished game after it's released, as well as any updates that may follow, but at a discounted price! The finished game will be sold for $20, so you get a discount for paying early. Your name will also go in the credits as an "Extra Special Owner."

SPECIAL OWNER - You'll get the finished game after it's released, as well as any updates that may follow. The finished game will be sold for $20, so you get a discount by helping to support the game.  Your name will also go in the credits as a "Special Owner."
BETA TESTER - You get the game after we reach a beta version. Your name will go in the credits as a "Beta Tester," and your feedback will shape the way the rest of the game is developed.

ALPHA TESTER - You get the game before anyone else.  As soon as we can, we will release the game to our Alpha supporters, and continue to provide them with weekly builds until the game is finished.  You have the opportunity to provide opinions at such an early stage in the development that your input will have a large impact on the direction of the game.  Your name will also go in the credits under "Alpha Supporter."

EARLYBIRD SKYPE - You get an early bird price (%50 off) at a one hour Skype session with us, the developers.  We can talk about anything you want, whenever we can, for one hour.  We'll even show you some behind-the-scenes in game developing if you want. It's your choice! Your name will go in the credits as an "Earlybird Skyper." (This pack includes the Alpha Tester tier)

SKYPE SUPPORTER - You get the regular price for a one hour Skype session with us, the developers.  We can talk about anything you want, whenever we can, for one hour.  We'll even show you some behind-the-scenes in game developing if you want. It's your choice! Your name will go in the credits as a "Skype Supporter." (This pack includes the Alpha Tester tier)

ROLE-MODEL - You get to be IN THE GAME! We will model a character after you and create the option to select your character in the game.  Now you can be in your first video game!  Your name will go in the credits in the cast list as one of the models. DISCLOSURE: You must provide us with certain photos of yourself if you want us to model after you. (This pack includes the Alpha Tester tier)

NAME THE CHARACTER - You get to choose the name for our character!  This tier is limited to only one person, so whatever you pick (within reason), we'll use!  You can use your own name, or anything else!  You will go in the credits under "Creative Developer." (This pack includes the Alpha Tester tier)

DINNER WITH US - You and a guest of your choosing can meet us in Philadelphia for dinner, on us! We'll take you to a nice, Philly restaurant and have a good time. For each additional guest, add $100. Your name will go in the credits in a special section for the high supporters.  (Transportation not included; This pack includes the Alpha Tester tier)

DESIGN A MODIFIER - You get to help us design a modifier to include in the game!  Examples of what we already have are: gravity, temperature, radiation, and electromagnetism.  YOU can help design a new one! We will incorporate it into our levels, and we can Skype or email as much as we need to discuss the specifics. You will go in the credits in a special place, as well as listed under "Creative Consultant." (This pack includes the Alpha Tester tier)

VISIT US - We will set a date where you can come and spend the day with us! You can see the office and learn the ins and outs of game developing.  But it's not all boring, cause we can play video games, you can help critique our game, and we will just hang out! Your name goes in a special place in the credits for high supporters, as well as under "Creative Consultant." (Transportation not included; This pack includes the Alpha Tester tier)
